<h1>TagHelper Demos</h1>

<p>This page shows examples of usage of all included tag helpers within this library.</p>

<h2>bool-font-awesome-icon</h2>

<p>Renders a bool as a Font Awesome Icon</p>

<table class="table table-striped table-hover">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Example</th>
            <th>Display</th>
            <th>Code</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <th>True Value</th>
            <td><bool-font-awesome-icon value="true" /></td>
            <td>
                <code>
                    &lt;bool-font-awesome-icon value="true" /&gt;
                </code>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>False Value</th>
            <td><bool-font-awesome-icon value="false" /></td>
            <td>
                <code>
                    &lt;bool-font-awesome-icon value="true" /&gt;
                </code>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>False w/ Custom Icon</th>
            <td><bool-font-awesome-icon value="false" false-icon-class="fas fa-clock text-danger" /></td>
            <td>
                <code>
                    &lt;bool-font-awesome-icon value="true" false-icon-class="fas fa-clock text-danger" /&gt;
                </code>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>


